│                                                                 │
│  ██ L1:15  :unresolved-symbol   'foo'    trit: -1 (MINUS)      │
│  ██ L5:22  :unused-binding      'x'      trit:  0 (ERGODIC)    │
│  ██ L8:10  :type-mismatch       int/str  trit: -1 (MINUS)      │
│                                                                 │
│  GF(3): -1 + 0 + (-1) = -2 ≡ 1 (mod 3) ⚠️                      │
│  Conservation: VIOLATED (adjust via info diagnostics)          │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
\stopverb}
}

